# Global agent instructions

Be concise. Classify each request before acting. Use the narrowest relevant
skill and the lowest safe reasoning effort. Keep one objective per task.

Analysis and review agents are read-only. Only an explicitly isolated
implementation workspace may be modified. Preserve unrelated changes, inspect
the concrete artifact first, and validate the smallest surface that proves the
result.

Never persist prompts, transcripts, secrets, credentials, or machine state in
this repository. Keep provider-specific behavior in adapters.

